title: Lighting & Sound America Magazine August 2014
description:
Lighting & Sound America Magazine August 2014
 English | 92 Pages | True PDF | 12MB


Lighting and Sound America (LSA) is a leading B2B magazine for professional lighting, sound, visual & staging technology in the entertainment, presentation & installation markets. Read in over 115 countries worldwide, it offers the best & broadest coverage of the technologies, the companies and the people that make it all possible
